          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-amber-600 mb-1">Gibibyte (GiB) — binary</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">1,073,741,824</p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">bytes = 1,024 × 1,024 × 1,024</p>
