      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Pick the capacity on the box; see the same bytes in every dialect.</p>
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 via-white to-indigo-50 border-2 border-gray-100">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6" aria-label="Drive sizes">
