            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-400 mb-1">📦 The box says</p>
            <p id="dd-box" class="text-xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">1 TB</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-1">decimal GB/TB</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-400 mb-1">🪟 Windows shows</p>
            <p id="dd-win" class="text-xl font-extrabold text-indigo-600">931.32 "GB"</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-1">binary math, GB label — really GiB</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-400 mb-1">🍎 macOS shows</p>
            <p id="dd-mac" class="text-xl font-extrabold text-teal-600">1 TB</p>
